  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Polyrhythm Lab is a polyrhythm generator. It allows you to build infinite combinations of sounds and rhythms. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2862580/extras/01d701e0a5f6d7da31ab5f4030d4ee63.poster.avif?t=1761090806\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2862580/extras/01d701e0a5f6d7da31ab5f4030d4ee63.webm?t=1761090806\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2862580/extras/01d701e0a5f6d7da31ab5f4030d4ee63.mp4?t=1761090806\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Polyrhythm Lab creates stunning visualisations of the polyrhythms you design.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2862580/extras/f315c6078753e22aea7bcbacf13f94ee.poster.avif?t=1761090806\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2862580/extras/f315c6078753e22aea7bcbacf13f94ee.webm?t=1761090806\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2862580/extras/f315c6078753e22aea7bcbacf13f94ee.mp4?t=1761090806\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Polyrhythm Lab allows you to control the number of notes and chords, with control over each notes pitch, and rhythm pattern. You can modulate the global time, and global pitch.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2862580/extras/92c927305507b97762f61ec288304240.avif?t=1761090806\" width=600 height=338 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can import any wav file as a sample, and then there is inbuilt reverb and low pass filtering controls.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can even customise the layout to keep open only the parameters that you are tweaking.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2862580/extras/4b7967784715dc8cdca9af263ed70753.avif?t=1761090806\" width=600 height=338 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >On the visual end, you can control bloom, particles, the motion of the notes, as well as the shape. You can set them to any colour you like as well.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can even export your polyrhythms to MIDI, allowing them to be used in your DAW of choice.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Polyrhythm Lab is a polyrhythm generator. It allows you to build infinite combinations of sounds and rhythms. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2862580/extras/01d701e0a5f6d7da31ab5f4030d4ee63.poster.avif?t=1761090806\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2862580/extras/01d701e0a5f6d7da31ab5f4030d4ee63.webm?t=1761090806\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2862580/extras/01d701e0a5f6d7da31ab5f4030d4ee63.mp4?t=1761090806\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Polyrhythm Lab creates stunning visualisations of the polyrhythms you design.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2862580/extras/f315c6078753e22aea7bcbacf13f94ee.poster.avif?t=1761090806\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2862580/extras/f315c6078753e22aea7bcbacf13f94ee.webm?t=1761090806\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2862580/extras/f315c6078753e22aea7bcbacf13f94ee.mp4?t=1761090806\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Polyrhythm Lab allows you to control the number of notes and chords, with control over each notes pitch, and rhythm pattern. You can modulate the global time, and global pitch.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2862580/extras/92c927305507b97762f61ec288304240.avif?t=1761090806\" width=600 height=338 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can import any wav file as a sample, and then there is inbuilt reverb and low pass filtering controls.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can even customise the layout to keep open only the parameters that you are tweaking.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2862580/extras/4b7967784715dc8cdca9af263ed70753.avif?t=1761090806\" width=600 height=338 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >On the visual end, you can control bloom, particles, the motion of the notes, as well as the shape. You can set them to any colour you like as well.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can even export your polyrhythms to MIDI, allowing them to be used in your DAW of choice.</p>",
